com.hazelcast.cache

Enum BuiltInCacheMergePolicies

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<BuiltInCacheMergePolicies>
      • com.hazelcast.cache.BuiltInCacheMergePolicies
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<BuiltInCacheMergePolicies>

    public enum BuiltInCacheMergePolicies
extends Enum<BuiltInCacheMergePolicies>

    Enum that represents all built-in CacheMergePolicy implementations.

    Note: When a new built-in CacheMergePolicy is implemented, its definition should be added here also.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      HIGHER_HITS
      Cache merge policy that merges cache entry from source to destination cache if source entry has more hits than the destination one.
      LATEST_ACCESS
      Cache merge policy that merges cache entry from source to destination cache if source entry has been accessed more recently than the destination entry.
      PASS_THROUGH
      Cache merge policy that merges cache entry from source to destination directly.
      PUT_IF_ABSENT
      Cache merge policy that merges cache entry from source to destination if it does not exist in the destination cache.
